description.text: Builder offering $7, 000 toward Incentives! Closing Costs! Fencing! Blinds! Preferred lender will buy rate down 1% for 1 Year! Welcome to the charming Cedar Lane community in the heart of Norman, Oklahoma. This exceptional property offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic elegance. As you step inside, you'll immediately be greeted by the warmth of wood look tile flooring that extends throughout the main areas, creating a seamless and inviting atmosphere. Living space is designed for your lifestyle, featuring an open concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Natural light pours in through large windows, illuminating the space and creating a bright and airy ambiance. Whether you're relaxing with loved ones or entertaining guests, this open layout ensures a sense of togetherness and connectivity. Kitchen boasts sleek modern appliances, under cabinet lighting, quartz counter tops, ample countertop space, and a kitchen island. The adjacent dining area is perfectly positioned to enjoy meals while basking in the natural light. A stylish barn door adds a touch of character and privacy as it leads into the hallway, where you'll find the cozy and carpeted bedrooms. These bedrooms provide a tranquil retreat, each offering a comfortable space to unwind after a long day. The master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom, creating a private oasis for relaxation and a walk-in closet that leads directly into the laundry room. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends, the covered patio and outdoor area provides the perfect backdrop for enjoying the Oklahoma breeze and serene views. Beyond the confines of your new home, you'll appreciate the convenience of easy access to the highway, making your daily commute a breeze. For students and academics, the proximity to the University of Oklahoma's campus is a major advantage, allowing you to effortlessly navigate your academic pursuits.
